            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><br><br><h5> This article is reformatted from originally published at <a href="https://betterprogramming.pub/the-one-programming-language-to-rule-them-all-620366df2805"><strong>TDS(Towards Data Science)</strong></a></h5></br><h5> <a href="https://medium.com/@ericmgirouard?source=post_page-----620366df2805--------------------------------">Author : Eric Girouard</a> </h5></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content4 cid-tt5SM2WLsM" id="content4-2" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
            <div class="container">
